Nagakura's daughter...."Aoi, everyone is ALWAYS bossing me around, 
especially that Kondou brat and Hijikata's girl thinks she's better 
than everyone"

Aoi (always too busy for the little people) walks away from 
Nagakura's daughter

Miki (Itou's princess) puts arm around Nagakura's daughter "Say, 
let's go hang out at the new club in town"

Nagakura's daughter (looking innocent) "but we're not old enough to"

Miki "don't worry I have some fake IDs and we can have Motoko bring 
us some smokes too"

Fujita Motoko listens to Nagakura's daughter and notes everything in 
her PDA...to report to her superiors.
----------
I hope someone designs Shimada Kai's daughter because she can inherit 
her father's love for sweets

I'm not suggesting that any possible storylines for *our* special 
version of Moeyoken follow shinsengumi history (that would make 
things boring)...it's just so fun to imagine every situation with 
teenage girls (^_^)
